what is the best way to describe how braxton hicks feel i am weeks and for about weeks now i have been having menstrual type cramps almost daily sometimes a couple times a day i have heard that bh can feel like cramps but i'm just wondering what other people felt how you would describe them thanks i was also unsure what was going on when i was cramping too my doc told me that low cramping like period cramps was probably my cervix changing she told me that braxton hicks contractions felt like the muscles contracting to hug the baby i was also told that my whole uterus might not always contract it might be just one side a quarter or the whole thing now that i'm farther along and i have more bh more frequently i agree with the hug the baby description congrats and good luck Pregnancy Cramp Miscarriage Menstrual cycle Fertility awareness Childbirth Breech birth Premature birth Urinary incontinence Androgen insensitivity syndrome Menstrual cup Uterus Endometriosis Sexual reproduction Endometrial cancer Cervix Gonorrhoea Care Bears Father's Day (Doctor Who) Obstetrics Fetal development Muscle Sharon Tate Toni Braxton Slow Train Coming Hormone replacement therapy (trans) Care-a-lot's Birthday Grumpy's Three Wishes Oral contraceptive Female reproductive system (human) The Care Bears Adventure in Wonderland Hysterectomy Friends Non-Hodgkin's lymphoma Intersex surgery Diazepam Physical intimacy I Want to Hold Your Hand Tetany Sex organ Similarities between the Bible and the Qur'an Episodes of Lost (Season 1) The Jazz Singer Equine conformation The Price Is Right Intact dilation and extraction Wild at Heart (Buffy episode) Intrauterine device Abortion The Caves of Androzani Marilyn Monroe The Care Bears (television series) Niddah Dysmenorrhea Le Malade imaginaire Weight training Lawrence v. Texas Haven (TNG episode) Social rule Infantilism Sam Cooke UK Singles Chart Love In vitro fertilisation Good Times Wrestlecrap Professional wrestling holds Ages of Myst Roswell UFO inciden